    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in wonderful shape, just waiting to hit the road for its next adventure. It drives smooth, looks great, and I\u2019ve really loved taking care of it. If you're looking for a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to go, you\u2019ve found it! I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how great it is!",
