    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension retains its factory-intended kinematics with refreshed bushings and dampers. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain razor-sharp. A true enthusiast's machine optimized for peak longitudinal and lateral performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
