    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. Honestly, I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this beauty! It\u2019s been incredibly reliable and is still in really wonderful shape\u2014it's clearly been well-loved and looked after. It runs like a dream and is just waiting for someone new to take it on some fun adventures. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
